# React Landing Page with Sign Up / Login

A medium-large single-page React application with a landing page (6 sections) and additional Sign Up and Login pages.  
Implemented client-side routing using React Router and basic form validation.  
Built reusable components and structured the application using modern React best practices.

# Live Demo
(https://frontend-portfolio-react-website.netlify.app/)

# Features
- Large landing page (6 sections: navigation, hero, multiple body sections, footer)
- Sign Up & Login pages (client-side validation)
- Component-based architecture
- Responsive design for desktop.
- Clean and maintainable code structure

# How to Run Locally
1. Clone the repository:
   bash
   git clone https://github.com/Z1g1e/portfolio-React.js
